                    <ab>(S.) In nomine domini Dei eterni. Anno ab incarnacione domini nostri Iesu
                        Christi millesimo C XX, octavo kalendas septembris, indicione tercia X.
                        Constat nos <persName key="#childOf #marriage #Venditio #Houses #Cereals #Legumes #Wine #Hay/fodder #Animals #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Mills #Fisheries #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"><name
                                ref="Martinus/de Rivale">Martinus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#childOf">filius</rs> quondam <persName key="#parentOf"><name
                                ref="Bertaldus">Bertaldi</name></persName> de <placeName
                            key="#Villas" ref="#places/4434">Rivale</placeName> et <persName
                                key="#marriage #Venditio #Houses #Cereals #Legumes #Wine #Hay/fodder #Animals #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Mills #Fisheries #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"><name ref="Gratia">Gracia</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#marriage">iugales</rs>, <persName key="#childOf #Venditio"><name
                            ref="Vivianus/de Rivale #Houses #Cereals #Legumes #Wine #Hay/fodder #Animals #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Mills #Fisheries #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">Vivianus</name></persName> filius noster,
                        qui professi sumus nos lege vivere <rs key="#Roman">Romana</rs>, ipso iugale
                        meo mihi consentientem et subter confirmantem, acepissemus nos qui supra
                        iugalibus et filius noster comuniter sicuti et in presentia <rs
                            key="#Witness">testium</rs> accepimus a te <persName key="#Venditio #Houses #Cereals #Legumes #Wine #Hay/fodder #Animals #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Mills #Fisheries #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                                ><name ref="Dominicus/de Gumpo">Dominicus de Gumpo</name></persName>
                        inter argentum et aliam rem valentem usque ad <rs key="#Price">libras centum
                            Veneciarum monete</rs>, finito precio sicut inter nos convenit,
                        nominative pro cunctis casis et omnibus rebus inmobilibus iuris nostris que
                        nos abere et possidere visi sumus in <geogName key="#Comitatus"
                            ref="#estates/125"><rs key="#Comitatus">comitatu</rs>
                            <placeName key="#Comitatus" ref="#places/13"
                            >Tervisiano</placeName></geogName> et infra fine de <rs key="#Villas"
                            >villa</rs> que dicitur Rivale, tam infra ipsa villa Rivale quamque et
                        de foris in eis finibus et territorio, secundum quod nobis pater filius
                        Gracia iugalibus pertinet per successionie per vel per <rs key="#Cartula"
                            >cartula aquisicionis</rs> aut per <rs key="#Offersio/donatio">cartula
                            donacionis</rs> vel aliquo modo ut dictum est, tam <rs key="#Houses"
                            >casis</rs> cum <rs key="#Cereals #Legumes">sediminibus seu terris
                            arabilibus</rs>, vigris, <rs key="#Wine">vineis</rs>, campis, <rs
                            key="#Hay/fodder #Animals">pratis, pascuis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Forests #Wood">silvis ac stelariis</rs>, rupis, rupinis ac <rs
                            key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos">paludibus</rs>, <rs key="#Mills"
                            >molendinis</rs>, <rs key="#Fisheries">piscacionibus</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">venacionibus, cultis et
                            incultis, divisis et indivisis, una cum finibus, terminibus,
                            accessionibus et usibus aquarum aquarumque ductibus</rs>, cum omni iure
                        ac iacentiis et pertin[en]tiis a suprascriptis casis rebus immobilibus
                        pertinentibus in integro. Que autem suprascriptis casis et rebus inmobilibus
                        iuris nostris superius dictis una cum accessionibus et ingressoras eactum
                        seu cum superioribus et inferioribus suis qualiter superius legitur in
                        integro ab ac die tibi cui supra Dominico pro suprascripto precio vendimus,
                        tradimus et mancipamus, nulli alii vendita, donata, alienata, obnoxiata vel
                        tradita nisi tibi, faciendum exinde a presenti die tu heredes tui aut cui tu
                        dederis iure proprietario nomine quicquid volueritis sine omni nostra et
                        heredum nostrorum contradicione. Quidem exspondimus atque promittimus nos
                        qui supra iugalibus Vivianus una cum nostris heredibus tibi cui supra
                        Dominicus tuisque heredibus aut cui vos dederitis suprascriptam vendicionern
                        qualiter superius legitur in integro ab omni homine defensare. Quod si
                        defendere non potuerimus aut vobis exinde aliquid per quovis ingenium
                        subtraere quesierimus, tunc <rs key="#Penalty">in duplum</rs> eandem
                        vendicionem ut supra legitur sicut pro tempore fuerit mehorata aut valuerit
                        sub exstimacione in consimili loco; et nec nobis liceat ullo tempore nolle
                        quod voluimus set quod a nobis semel factum vel conscriptum est, sub ius
                        iurandum inviolabiliter conservare promitimus cum stipulacione subnixa, et
                        nichil nobis ex ipso precio aliquid reddebere diximus. Actum in villa Rivale
                        feliciter. Signum +++++++++ manu suprascriptis iugalibus qui hanc cartulam
                        vendicionis fieri rogaverunt et suprascripto precio acceperunt ut supra.
                        Signum +++++++++++++++ manu <persName key="#Witness #Venditio #siblingOf"
                                ><name ref="Iohannes Bonus">Iohannes Bonus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#siblingOf">frater</rs>
                        <persName key="#siblingOf"><name ref="Aribrandus"
                            >Ariprandi</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Venditio #childOf"><name ref="Adam"
                            >Adam</name></persName> filius <persName key="#parentOf"><name
                                ref="Amelricus">Amelrici</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Venditio"><name ref="Ingelerius/de Vigodarzere"
                                >Ingelero</name></persName> de <placeName ref="#places/4436"
                            >Vigodarzere</placeName>, <persName key="#Witness #Venditio"><name
                                ref="Arimonius">Arimeno</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#nephew/nieceOf">nepos</rs>
                        <persName><name ref="Dominicus">Dominici</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Venditio"><name ref="Kazelus">Kazeli</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness #Venditio"><name ref="Aldebrandus/de Vigonza"
                                >Aldevrando</name></persName> de <placeName ref="#places/4436"
                            >Vigonza</placeName> omnes istis in ac cartula vendicionis rogatorum
                        testium. (S.) Ego <persName key="#Notary #Writer #Venditio"><name
                                ref="Iohannes">Iohannes</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> Sacri Palacii <rs key="#Writer"
                            >scriptor</rs> huius <rs key="#Venditio">cartula vendicionis</rs> pos[t]
                        tradita complevi et dedi. </ab>
                </div>
